cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SE 

This paper is about intrusion detection systems (IDSs) for IoT networks using machine learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also focuses on evaluating the performance of various machine learning classifiers, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with IoT networks, which could place it in cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of machine learning algorithms also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the quality of the datasets used, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering).
